OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1783521453
OL,3,CCCTV released one year after man found
OL,4,Cdead in Cornish woods
OL,6,FNew CCTV images have been released one
OL,7,Fyear after a man was found dead in
OL,8,Fwoodland in Cornwall.
OL,10,FA major enquiry was launched after 50-
OL,11,Fyear-old Lee Hockey's body was found
OL,12,Fbetween Truro and Probus at around 6pm
OL,13,Fon 1 July 2025.
OL,15,FDevon and Cornwall Police is launching
OL,16,Fan anniversary appeal with images of
OL,17,Fhim in the days before he was found.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
