PN,40302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1783521453
OL,3,CCCTV released one year after man found
OL,4,Cdead in Cornish woods
OL,6,FHis death is being treated as
OL,7,Funexplained by the Force's Major Crime
OL,8,FInvestigation Team. According to
OL,9,Fpolice, murder is one potential
OL,10,Fhypothesis detectives continue to
OL,11,Ffully investigate.
OL,13,FExtensive enquiries and searches have
OL,14,Fbeen carried out to establish the
OL,15,Fcircumstances of Lee's death and to
OL,16,Ftrace his final movements. The last-
OL,17,Fconfirmed sighting of Lee was in the
OL,18,FTrispen area on 23 June 2025.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1783521453
OL,3,CCCTV released one year after man found
OL,4,Cdead in Cornish woods
OL,6,FIn particular, the police force is
OL,7,Fasking for help to find a number of
OL,8,Fhis missing personal belongings. They
OL,9,Finclude a black satchel-style bag
OL,10,Fshown on the new CCTV pictures of Lee
OL,11,Ftaken at Tesco Express in Truro on 22
OL,12,FJune 2025.
OL,14,FHis passport and Barclays Bank card
OL,15,Fwith the full name "Lee Hockey" and a
OL,16,Fpink iPhone 13 are also missing.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
