OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1783521453
OL,3,CCCTV released one year after man found
OL,4,Cdead in Cornish woods
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Rob Smith
OL,7,Fsaid: "Lee's family are marking the
OL,8,Fone-year anniversary of his loss and
OL,9,Fstill have many unanswered questions
OL,10,Fabout the lead-up to his death.
OL,12,F"While we are very grateful for the
OL,13,Fhelp we have received from the public
OL,14,Fso far, we still believe that someone
OL,15,Fout there could hold critical
OL,16,Finformation to help us find out what
OL,17,Fhappened to him.
OL,26,@oD@GOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1783521453
OL,3,CCCTV released one year after man found
OL,4,Cdead in Cornish woods
OL,6,F"Some of Lee's personal belongings
OL,7,Fremain outstanding and we are urging
OL,8,Fanyone who may have either found or
OL,9,Fseen these crucial items to get in
OL,10,Ftouch. They could contain vital
OL,11,Finformation to help our investigation
OL,12,Finto Lee's death, and we urge you to
OL,13,Fcome forward."
OL,15,FDetectives have pieced together Lee's
OL,16,Fknown movements in the days before his
OL,17,Fdeath.
OL,19,FHe spent most of Monday 23 June in
OL,20,FTruro city centre before taking a bus
OL,21,Fout to the Trispen area.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@NO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
