PN,40306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1783521453
OL,3,CCCTV released one year after man found
OL,4,Cdead in Cornish woods
OL,6,FThe last confirmed sighting of Lee was
OL,7,Fin Trispen later that evening. His
OL,8,Fwhereabouts from there are currently
OL,9,Funknown, but it is likely he would
OL,10,Fhave been on foot.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
