PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1783521453
OL,3,CCCTV released one year after man found
OL,4,Cdead in Cornish woods
OL,6,FLee's family said in a statement: "We
OL,7,Fthe family of Lee Hockey are thankful
OL,8,Ffor all the support over the last 12
OL,9,Fmonths but are still looking for
OL,10,Fclosure over what happened to him.
OL,12,F"If anyone has any information, no
OL,13,Fmatter how small, please come forward.
OL,15,F"Lee would have been watching the
OL,16,FWorld Cup this year and was a keen
OL,17,FArsenal supporter. We would also like
OL,18,Fto thank all of the police for the
OL,19,Fgruelling task of searching the woods
OL,20,Fand ponds for Lee's missing bag."
OL,26,@nD@cOUtD@AOUwD@AOU|D@aO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
